					&lt;p&gt;Now I know you could put any whiskey and any beer together and it'd still be a boilermaker, but I'm wanting to find a pairing that works quite nicely - a dark ale and a smokey scotch? A pale ale and an Irish whiskey? As fun as it would be try every combo, I only have so much beer and so much whiskey, and could use a jump start.&lt;/p&gt;

					&lt;p&gt;I am Australian by the way, so I might not be able to get my hands on any particularly specific recommendations.&lt;/p&gt;

